[752.003328, "o", "GREP(1)            User Commands            GREP(1)\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mNAME\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       grep, egrep, fgrep, rgrep - print lines that\u001b[m\r\n       match patterns\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mSYNOPSIS\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mgrep\u001b[0m [\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m...] \u001b[4mPATTERNS\u001b[24m [\u001b[4mFILE\u001b[24m...]\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mgrep\u001b[0m [\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m...] \u001b[1m-e\u001b[0m \u001b[4mPATTERNS\u001b[24m ... [\u001b[4mFILE\u001b[24m...]\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mgrep\u001b[0m   [\u001b[4mOPTION\u001b[24m...]   \u001b[1m-f\u001b[0m   \u001b[4mPATTERN_FILE\u001b[24m   ...\u001b[m\r\n       [\u001b[4mFILE\u001b[24m...]\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[1mDESCRIPTION\u001b[0m\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[1mgrep\u001b[0m  searches  for  \u001b[4mPATTERNS\u001b[24m  in each \u001b[4mFILE\u001b[24m.\u001b[m\r\n       \u001b[4mPATTERNS\u001b[24m is one or more  patterns  separated\u001b[m\r\n       by  newline characters, and \u001b[1mgrep\u001b[0m prints each\u001b[m\r\n       line  that  matches  a  pattern.   Typically\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7mpage grep(1) line 1 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
